'''Merl's''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located in [[Muracie]] on [[Centares/Legends|Centares]]. It was owned by [[Merl]]. Food from Merl's was smuggled to [[Tyler Lucian]]. Merl and his bouncers, [[Glocken]] and [[Uri]], were killed in a firefight with [[Beilert Valance/Legends|Beilert Valance]], when the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] tried to get Merl to reveal the hiding place of Lucian.<ref name="marvel29">[[Star Wars (1977) 29|''Star Wars'' (1977) 29]]</ref>

